{"tid":2423641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國證券報：MPF管理機構洽商放寬投資A股","createTime":"2021-02-26T04:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T04:39:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"27bf5a1f0f79ef1070171457d60be64ab18fd134","tid":2423641,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"《中國證券報》報道，香港MPF管理機構近期正在與中國監管機構商議，希望將滬深交易所的A股股票加入投資組合，以增加收益。香港監管機構在2020年底放開了香港「強積金」投資內地股市的限制，該社指香港不少投資機構對此非常感興致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210226/YALSNRMDBND4FKDIZUK3D5UB7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210226%2FYALSNRMDBND4FKDIZUK3D5UB7M%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd62a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=36c2994d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210226%2FYALSNRMDBND4FKDIZUK3D5UB7M%2F&h=86925f5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210226/YALSNRMDBND4FKDIZUK3D5UB7M/</a>"}]}